tableInfo.caption: 入库明细
tableInfo.sql: SELECT T_JH_ZL.MC AS ZLMC,T_JH_JX.MC AS JXMC,T_CK_CRKQD.*, T_CK_CK.BBZ,T_XT_BZLB.MC AS BZMC,T_XT_HCLB.MC AS HCLBMC,T_JH.MC JHMC,T_XT_JLDW.MC JLDW, T_CK_CK.GLFS,T_CK_CK.SFRLQ,T_CK_CK.ZRLQ,YFRQ AS YFQZ FROM T_CK_CRKQD LEFT JOIN T_JH_ZL ON T_JH_ZL.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.ZL LEFT JOIN T_JH_JX ON T_JH_JX.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.JX LEFT JOIN T_CK_CK ON T_CK_CK.DWID=T_CK_CRKQD.DWID AND T_CK_CRKQD.JH=T_CK_CK.JH AND T_CK_CK.XH = T_CK_CRKQD.XH LEFT JOIN T_XT_BZLB ON T_XT_BZLB.ID=T_CK_CK.BBZ LEFT JOIN T_JH ON T_JH.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.JH LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW ON T_XT_JLDW.ID=T_JH.DW LEFT JOIN T_XT_HCLB ON T_XT_HCLB.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.HCLB WHERE 1=1

tableInfo.caption: 发付清单
tableInfo.sql: SELECT QD.BH, QD.JX, WH, JH, T_JH.MC JHMC, JL.MC JLDW, XH, SL, T_JH_ZL.MC ZL, DJ, ZJ, CCRQ, YSRQ, SMZT, RKRQ, ZSMN, ZSMXS, ZSMXH, ZSMQL, ZFXCS, YFRQ, FXRQ, FXSMN, FXSMXS, FXCS, SBQXN, SBQXXS, BZ, ZFXXS, BCZFXXS, BCFXXS, ZXHCS, BCZXHCS, BCXHCS, ZQLCS, BCZQLCS, BCQLCS, CJRQ, YFCS, ZYFCS, XSBZ, XZ, QD.HL, DWID, LB, RQ, JJ, HCLB, BBZ, BZ.MC BZMC, ZYLB, ZGQCS, GQCS, YFQX, JXQN, JXQXS, RFID, YSID , T_JH.GLFS FROM T_SQLITE_FFQD QD LEFT JOIN T_JH_ZL ON QD.ZL=T_JH_ZL.ID LEFT JOIN T_SQLITE_FF ON QD.BH=T_SQLITE_FF.BH LEFT JOIN T_JH ON T_JH.ID=QD.JH AND T_JH.JX= QD.JX LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW JL ON JL.ID = T_JH.DW LEFT JOIN T_XT_BZLB BZ ON BZ.ID=QD.BBZ WHERE 1=1 ORDER BY BH
